715144f-a.title: Manhattan: 116th Street (West) - Manhattan Avenue
715144f-a.text:
West 116th Street, east from but not including Manhattan Ave., showing
the roadway after the removal of street car tracks. Note the Sixth and
Ninth Aves. Elevated Lines on Eighth Ave. at this point.
January 4, 1937.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
